text: I love the Tecate Quesadilla chicken or beef it's the best I've ever had, a bit pricey but worth it (it comes with alot of sour cream and guac so if you aren't a big fan get it on the side)
Excellent tacos and burritos!!!! Try them and you will fall in love with this place.

Hole in the wall, with great food prepared
after you order. The carne asada burrito is awesome.
